The alien race that started the kidnapping plot thought that Matt Damon was considered a "National Treasure", the plan was already underway when they realized it wasn't Matt Damon, but some other random guy that was kidnapped.

A letter is sent to the President of the United States of America requesting that the alien race receives $10,000,000 in exchange for Matt Damon. The president, understandably upset about incident, reached out to his Hollywood contacts and what does he discover? Matt Damon is home with his family and is completely oblivious about the entire incident. 

The officials are put on the case to see who exactly was kidnapped. Careful that they didn't  make the aliens aware that they had the wrong person as well as the human race as a whole aware that aliens kidnapped one of their own. 

After a full 24 hours of looking into the matter, the Beverly Hills police got a strange call. An actor had gone missing, but was returned after 12 hours telling a very confusing tale. The actor wasn't Matt Damon or anyone related to him. It was Mark Wahlberg. 
The aliens, realizing that they had in fact kidnapped the wrong human being, had already returned Mark Wahlberg to his home. and were far from Earth
 he incident is now on the cover of every newspaper, news channel and the story of an alien abduction has gone viral.

The alien race that started the kidnapping plot thought that Matt Damon was considered a "National Treasure", the plan was already underway when they realized it wasn't Matt Damon, but some other random guy that was kidnapped.

A letter is sent to the President of the United States of America requesting that the alien race receives $10,000,000 in exchange for Matt Damon. The president, understandably upset about incident, reached out to his Hollywood contacts and what does he discover? Matt Damon is home with his family and is completely oblivious about the entire incident. 

The officials are put on the case to see who exactly was kidnapped. Careful that they didn't  make the aliens aware that they had the wrong person as well as the human race as a whole aware that aliens kidnapped one of their own. 

After a full 24 hours of looking into the matter, the Beverly Hills police got a strange call. An actor had gone missing, but was returned after 12 hours telling a very confusing tale. The actor wasn't Matt Damon or anyone related to him. It was Mark Wahlberg. 
The aliens, realizing that they had in fact kidnapped the wrong human being, had already returned Mark Wahlberg to his home. and were far from Earth
 he incident is now on the cover of every newspaper, news channel and the story of an alien abduction has gone viral.
